items.title: Awesome Shell
items.content_text:
### Command-Line Productivity

*   [boom (⭐1.3k)](https://github.com/holman/boom) - Store links and snippets in the command line
*   [cod (⭐535)](https://github.com/dim-an/cod) — A completion daemon for shell that learns when you invoke `--help` commands
*   [dnote (⭐2.9k)](https://github.com/dnote/dnote) - A simple command line notebook with multi-device sync and web interface
*   [foxy (⭐44)](https://github.com/s-p-k/foxy) - Plain text bookmarks for Firefox and surf browsers.
*   [resh (⭐1k)](https://github.com/curusarn/resh) - Contextual shell history for Zsh and Bash
*   [snips (⭐85)](https://github.com/srijanshetty/snips) - Command line tool to manage snippets of code.

### For Developers / Directory Navigation

*   [mkdkr (⭐378)](https://github.com/rosineygp/mkdkr) - Makefile + Docker = CI Pipeline

### Downloading and Serving / Directory Navigation

*   [bashhub-server (⭐312)](https://github.com/nicksherron/bashhub-server) - Private cloud shell history. Open source server for bashhub
